<task id="access_grafana_zosmf" xml:lang="en-us">
    <title>Accessing the Grafana dashboard</title>
    <shortdesc>You can access the Grafana dashboard from the <wintitle>Resource
            Monitoring</wintitle> page of <ph conref="conref.dita#conref/zosmf_short"/> to
        investigate the RMF Monitor III metrics and reports.</shortdesc>
    <taskbody>
        <prereq id="prereq_apk_dbm_syb">You must have defined the Grafana server in <ph
                conref="conref.dita#conref/zosmf_short"/>. See <xref
                href="define_grafana_zosmf.dita"/>.</prereq>
        <steps>
            <step>
                <cmd><ph conref="conref.dita#conref/ph_i51_xbm_syb"/></cmd>
            </step>
            <step>
                <cmd><ph conref="conref.dita#conref/ph_pfq_bcm_syb"/></cmd>
            </step>
            <step>
                <cmd>Double-click <uicontrol>Resource Monitoring</uicontrol>.</cmd>
            </step>
            <step>
                <cmd>Select the Grafana server that you want to access from the drop-down
                    list.</cmd>
            </step>
            <step>
                <cmd>Click <uicontrol>OK</uicontrol>.</cmd>
            </step>
        </steps>
        <result id="result_d3m_qcm_syb">You have accessed Grafana from <ph
                conref="conref.dita#conref/zosmf_short"/>.</result>
        <postreq id="postreq_dzr_rcm_syb"><ph conref="conref.dita#conref/ph_cyy_4bm_syb"/><ul
                id="ul_uhg_tcm_syb">
                <li>View the dashboards by navigating to <menucascade>
                        <uicontrol>Apps</uicontrol>
                        <uicontrol>IBM RMF</uicontrol>
                        <uicontrol>Dashboards</uicontrol>
                    </menucascade>.</li>
                <li>Add a RMF data source to fetch data from <ph
                        conref="conref.dita#conref/dds_full"/>s (<ph
                        conref="conref.dita#conref/dds_short"/>). See <xref
                        href="about:blankcreate_datasources.dita" format="dita" scope="external"
                        >Creating RMF data sources</xref>.</li>
            </ul></postreq>
    </taskbody>
</task>
